description: Let a_0 = 1 and for n > 0, let a_n be the smallest positive integer not already in the sequence such that (a_0 + a_1 x + a-2x^2 + ....)^(1/3) has integer coefficients. (Hanna's A083349). Let f(n) = n th term in the present sequence. Then a_0 + a_1 x + a_2 x^2 + ... = (1-x)^f(1) (1-x^2)^f(2) (1-x^3)^f(3) ....
